cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it as below, and see the "Citing this work" section of README.md for the underlying SuStaIn methodology papers to cite as well.
type: software
title: mv-sustain
version: 0.1.2
date-released: "2026-07-08"
abstract: >-
  A longitudinal, multi-visit extension of the SuStaIn (Subtype and Stage Inference) algorithm, built on pySuStaIn, adding a joint patient-level likelihood for cohorts with repeated visits per patient.
authors:
