    title: "Uncovering the heterogeneity and temporal complexity of neurodegenerative diseases with Subtype and Stage Inference"
    authors:
      - family-names: Young
        given-names: Alexandra L.
    year: 2018
    journal: Nature Communications
    doi: 10.1038/s41467-018-05892-0
  - type: article
    title: "pySuStaIn: A Python implementation of the Subtype and Stage Inference algorithm"
    authors:
